Privacy Impact Assessment(PIA) - What would impact of privacy we were protecting got out.

Privacy Threshold Assessment(PTA) - doing Assessment on data, where is data? Where is storing the data.
A privacy threshold assessment (PTA) is a process that a company uses to analyze how personal information is protected within an IT system. 


Recovery time Objective (RTO) - minimum time necessary to restore the Critial system operation.

Recovery point Objective (RPO) - Maximum data that can be lost without substantial impact.

